platformAttributes.ios.editorialNotes.st.k: The world’s most ridiculous goat is back in this hilarious massively multiplayer online game. From the very start, it’s obvious this isn’t your typical MMO. It all begins with you choosing one of six classes—which run the gamut from Magician to Microwave (seriously)—then embarking on bizarre quests. Like its predecessors, the game comes chock full of meta jokes, lovably preserved glitches, and destructible environments while boasting incredibly impressive landscapes and entertaining gameplay.
